comments.body:
> Looking at mingw-w64, `GetACP` has returned `CP_UTF8` since it was introduced.

I see it differently. I've cross-compiled this code:
```c++
#include <iostream>
#include <windows.h>

int main()
{
    std::cout << GetACP() << "\n";
}
```

and it prints 1252 on Windows.
